		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2c62d3" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2c62d3">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="223" width="412" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人扔出纯水制成的标枪，落地造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%</span><span>伤害，并产生内外2层激波，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">60%</span><span>伤害，可连续施放3次；<br/></span><span color="#9999ff">强化：</span><span>伤害倍率提升，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="511" width="408" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人用左手拍向玩家，造成<span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="437" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人旋转纯水制成的榔锤，进行3次攻击，依次造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%,62.5%,65%</span><span>伤害；第三段攻击产生激波，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#9999ff">强化：</span><span>伤害倍率提升，挥舞造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%,92.5%,95%</span><span>伤害，不产生激波。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="438" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人蓄力，附属<span textDecoration="underline">白盾</span><span>；12s后白盾消失，幻人掀起澜海激潮，在场地内下起小雨，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">20%</span><span>伤害；溅起的潮水凝结成3把水枪，并一起在自身周围降下，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害，并产生一道冲击波引爆所有半幻人，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害，冲击波将会</span><span color="#ffbfbf">秒杀</span><span>在场非无敌状态的角色。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">场地内将不断生成<span textDecoration="underline">半幻人</span><span>，数量维持在3个；在战斗中水形幻人会吸收所有半幻人，施放4个技能或进行瞬移后结束强化状态。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="431" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人挥舞纯水制成的短刀，进行2次攻击，依次造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%,65%</span><span>伤害；第一段攻击产生剑气，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#9999ff">强化：</span><span>伤害倍率提升，挥舞造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%,95%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
