		<RichText x="66" y="1068" width="430" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">半幻人：<span color="#7fbfff">4.8水</span><span>盾，击破后消失；其继承幻人28%的攻击力。<br/>白盾：依词条数目，继承9.35%/11.69%/10.79%/14.76%/<br/>23.38%生命值，破坏后扣除幻人护盾等量生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
